summary: Adds Ulfrics Children Yjara and Yjan to the Palace of Kings, they can follow you and have the same power their father has as well.
descriptionHtml:
Adds the prince and the princess of Skyrim.

Yjara and Yjan will sit in the Palace of Kings and wait for you. They\'re both marriable and use the Unrelenting Force Shout, their names may be german ;). Yjara is a level 50 Assassin and Yjan is a level 50 barbarian. 
Don\'t be disappointed, they both have got more from their motherthan from their father.
author: JacquesMo
